sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant M as Mobile App
    participant B as Backend API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant AI as Mock AI Gateway

    U->>M: Open app
    M->>M: Onboarding form
    U->>M: Fill profile
    M->>B: POST /learner-profile
    B->>DB: INSERT learner_profiles
    DB-->>B: Profile created
    B-->>M: ProfileResponse
    M->>B: POST /diagnostics/sessions
    B->>DB: INSERT diagnostic_session
    B-->>M: CreateSessionResponse

    loop 4 diagnostic steps
        U->>M: Submit response
        M->>B: POST /diagnostics/sessions/{id}/responses
        B->>DB: INSERT diagnostic_response
        B-->>M: SubmitResponseResponse
    end

    M->>B: POST /diagnostics/sessions/{id}/complete
    B->>DB: SELECT all responses
    B->>B: _assess_responses() → CEFR
    B->>DB: INSERT skill_assessments
    B->>DB: UPDATE diagnostic_session → COMPLETED
    B-->>M: CompleteSessionResponse

    M->>B: GET /learning-contract/current
    B->>DB: SELECT or CREATE learning_entry_contract
    B-->>M: ContractResponse

    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions
    B->>DB: INSERT lesson_session
    B-->>M: SessionResponse

    U->>M: Write narrative text
    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions/{id}/submissions
    B->>DB: INSERT submission
    B-->>M: SubmitTextResponse

    M->>B: POST /lesson-sessions/{id}/process
    B->>DB: SELECT submission
    B->>B: State: SUBMITTED → ANALYSIS_PENDING
    B->>AI: analyze_submission()
    AI-->>B: Analysis result (deterministic)
    B->>B: Linguistic validation
    B->>B: Pedagogical validation
    B->>B: Policy decision → COMPLETE
    B->>DB: INSERT validation_results
    B->>DB: UPDATE session → COMPLETED
    B->>DB: INSERT mastery_evidence
    B-->>M: ProcessResponse (status: COMPLETED)

    M->>M: Navigate to result screen
